The company-wide Healthy and Safe @ Siemens program1 Our company-wide Healthy and Safe @ Siemens (HS @ S)

program invites employees to help shape leadership, learn from each other, increase well-being at work, and promote innovations and improvements in occupational health and safety. It is based on five principles:

~

We care for our own and each other’s well-being.

¥

We speak up and take part in making the workplace healthier and safer.

“

We are inclusive and invite a diverse range of views on health and safety.